question: feedback
answer: With the sound check at the start, I set my volume low initially since the initial static noise sound was very grating on my ears. Because my sound was low I could not tell with the first check which sound was quietest of the three. I think you should use a different noise at the start, maybe of a person speaking, to check the volume and not a loud static noise.
